sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant IndividualProvidedDetailsController
    participant HMRC_Auth as HMRC Auth
    participant MongoDB as MongoDB (individual)

    Client->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: GET /individual-provided-details/for-application/{agentApplicationId}
    IndividualProvidedDetailsController->>HMRC_Auth: Authenticate (GG, Agent affinity)
    alt Auth fails
        HMRC_Auth-->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: 401 Unauthorised
        IndividualProvidedDetailsController-->>Client: 401 Unauthorised
    else Auth succeeds
        HMRC_Auth-->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: Authenticated
        IndividualProvidedDetailsController->>MongoDB: find(agentApplicationId)
        MongoDB-->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: List[IndividualProvidedDetails] (may be empty)
        IndividualProvidedDetailsController-->>Client: 200 OK (JSON array)
    end
